<http://www.spektrix.com/chemainustheatrefestivalsociety/event/21004ACHSVCHPTJGKBPHSVBSBDSRRDPRT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Ladies Foursome";
  schema:description """
	APR 17 - MAY 17<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>by Norm Foster<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready to laugh and cry on the green with Norm Foster’s uproarious comedy, The Ladies Foursome! Four friends tee off in a full round of golf the day after a friend’s funeral - revealing long-kept secrets, hilarious confessions, and pining for love near and far.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Content Advisory:<span><br/></span>•	Recommended for ages 16+ <span><br/></span>•	Comedic discussions of mature themes, including sex and death<span><br/></span>•	Some course language and use of alcohol<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for lunch or dinner in the Playbill Dining Room! Dining can be added to your order after selecting your theatre tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h1><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://purchase.chemainustheatrefestival.ca/TicketSubscriptions\"> Subscriptions Available - ORDER NOW</a></h1>
""";
